    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the high-revving 3.6L M96/03 flat-six and a tactile G96 6-speed manual transaxle. This example is mechanically sorted, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal (RMS) replacement. The chassis retains its signature poise with factory-spec multi-link rear geometry and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers for consistent thermal management during spirited driving. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain remains robust, delivering 320 hp with a linear torque curve. An honest, driver-grade 911 for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
